Project Name: Gentoo x86 QA-website
Project Info: Google Summer of Code 2010 project
Maintainer: John-Patrik Nilsson
IRC nick: mindbug
email: themindbug@gmail.com


##############################
#### Website URL examples ####
##############################
The welcome view:           'simple_qa/'
The search view:            'simple_qa/search/'
The advanced search view:   'simple_qa/search/advanced/'
Browsing example:           'simple_qa/reports/x86/www-client/'
(See 'simple_qa/urls.py' for more information)


##########################
#### This is the Code ####
##########################
Django application name: simple_qa

Files:
URL configuration:  'simple_qa/urls.py'
Models:             'simple_qa/models.py'
Views:              'simple_qa/views.py'
Forms:              'simple_qa/forms.py'
Templates:          'templates/simple_qa/*'
CSS:                'site_media/css/*'
Graphics:           'site_media/gfx/*'


